Global All in One Cookers Market Insights
All in One Cookers Market size was valued at USD 5.12 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 9.08 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

All in One Cookers Market Overview
The All-in-One Cookers Market has seen substantial growth in recent years, reaching a market value of approximately USD 6.3 billion in 2024. The market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2025 to 2030, driven by increasing consumer preference for multifunctional kitchen appliances and time-saving cooking solutions. These devices combine multiple functions like pressure cooking, slow cooking, and steaming, making them highly popular among busy professionals and home chefs. The market's expansion is also bolstered by ongoing advancements in technology, enhancing user experience with smart features and improved energy efficiency.

